query:
SELECT id AS id,
       plan_id AS plan_id,
       plan_title AS plan_title,
       plan_name AS plan_name,
       plan_status AS plan_status,
       jurisdiction_id AS jurisdiction_id,
       plan_fi_status AS plan_fi_status,
       plan_fi_reason AS plan_fi_reason,
       plan_date AS plan_date,
       plan_effective_period_start AS plan_effective_period_start,
       plan_effective_period_end AS plan_effective_period_end,
       plan_intervention_type AS plan_intervention_type,
       plan_version AS plan_version,
       jurisdiction_parent_id AS jurisdiction_parent_id,
       jurisdiction_name AS jurisdiction_name,
       jurisdiction_depth AS jurisdiction_depth,
       jurisdiction_path AS jurisdiction_path,
       jurisdiction_name_path AS jurisdiction_name_path
FROM
  (SELECT id,
          plan_id,
          plan_title,
          plan_name,
          plan_status,
          jurisdiction_id,
          plan_fi_status,
          plan_fi_reason,
          plan_date,
          plan_effective_period_start,
          plan_effective_period_end,
          plan_intervention_type,
          plan_version,
          jurisdiction_parent_id,
          jurisdiction_name,
          jurisdiction_depth,
          jurisdiction_path,
          jurisdiction_name_path
   FROM public.plans_materialzied_view) AS expr_qry
WHERE plan_date >= '1920-06-16 00:00:00'
  AND jurisdiction_id = '3951'
LIMIT 10000;
